query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-ndk',
'buffer',
'cryptography',
'filesystems',
'grid',
'gson',
'ibm-cloud',
'microservices',
'ms-access-2010',
'office365',
'openssl',
'pipe',
'rx-java');
